description: Ingrid Mouth had an impressive debut on Ultimate Surrender when she beat an experienced, Andre Shakti. She is ranked as our #1 rookie this year and and is expected to win the rookie cup tournament. Today she is going to be made humble by Ariel X, who is so sure of herself she claims she could beat any rookie even while she is blind folded. Red, Syd Blackovich, calls Ariel out on this claim and a blind folded Match ensues.
title: Promising Rookie Gets a wake up call from Ariel X
